column2: Custom Photo Party Sash - Birthday, Bachelorette, Wedding
column3:
Custom photo & text party sash for birthdays, bachelorette parties, weddings, and more!
Turn your favorite picture and words into a keepsake birthday sash, bachelorette sash, or wedding party sash that actually feels special.

‚ú® What You'll Get
1 custom sash with your photo + personalized text
Perfect for:
Birthdays (21st, 30th, 40th, 50th, 60th & beyond)
Bachelorette parties & bridal showers
Bride-to-be / Future Mrs.
Graduations, retirements, work parties, themed events
Your sash arrives already connected (no awkward safety pins!), ready to wear straight out of the package.

üßµ Details
Material: Smooth satin-style ribbon (soft and comfortable to wear)
Width: Approx. 3 inch wide
Length: Sized to fit most adults comfortably (sash is sewn/secured in place)
Design: Your photo + custom wording printed directly onto the sash
Colors & fonts: I'll match the design style to your event (bold, elegant, fun, or spooky ‚Äì just tell me your vibe)
If you have very specific colors or fonts, mention them in the personalization box and I'll do my best to match.

üñº How to Personalize
Choose your quantity and add the sash to your cart.
In the personalization box, include:
The text you want (name, age, event, phrase, etc.)
Your event type (birthday / bachelorette / wedding / other)
Any style notes (girly, minimal, glam, spooky, goth, etc.)
After checkout, send me your photo via Etsy Messages:
Clear, high-resolution image (no screenshots if possible)
Good lighting works best
Let me know if you want it cropped a certain way
I'll design your sash using your image and wording and print it to order just for you.

üïí Processing & Shipping
Each sash is made to order.
Processing time: see the current estimate in the listing.
If you need it by a specific date, message me before ordering so I can confirm timing.

ü¶á Love Goth, Witchy, or Spooky Themes?
I also specialize in goth, witchy, and Halloween-inspired designs.
Ask for:
Black or dark-colored sash
Witchy fonts and motifs (moons, bats, stars, coffins, etc.)
Phrases like "Birthday Witch," "Goth Bride," "Til Death Bachelorette," and more
Leave your spooky ideas in the personalization box and I'll create a sash that matches your dark celebration.
